ea charts are useful for visualizing the trend of a numerical variable over time, especially when you want to emphasize the cumulative magnitude of change."],"metadata":{"id":"m2xqNkiQp1ck"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##### 2. What is/are the insight(s) found from the chart?"],"metadata":{"id":"ZWILFDl5p1ck"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["The filled area under the curve emphasizes the cumulative magnitude of change in the variable. This can help in understanding the overall impact or significance of the trend."],"metadata":{"id":"x-lUsV2mp1ck"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##### 3. Will the gained insights help creating a positive business impact?\n","Are there any insights that lead to negative growth? Justify with specific reason."],"metadata":{"id":"M7G43BXep1ck"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Yes, the insights gained from the area chart can contribute to a positive business impact by providing a clear understanding of the trend and magnitude of change in a numerical variable over time.\n","\n","While the area chart itself doesn't directly indicate negative growth, it can highlight potential areas of concern. If you find unexpected patterns or an increasing trend in a negative metric (e.g., crime rates or customer churn)"],"metadata":{"id":"5wwDJXsLp1cl"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#### Chart - 13"],"metadata":{"id":"Ag9LCva-p1cl"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["sns.pairplot(df, diag_kind='kde')\n","plt.show()"],"metadata":{"id":"EUfxeq9-p1cl"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##### 1. Why did you pick the specific chart?"],"metadata":{"id":"E6MkPsBcp1cl"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["A pair plot is an effective visualization tool for exploring relationships between multiple numerical variables in a dataset."],"metadata":{"id":"V22bRsFWp1cl"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##### 2. What is/are the insight(s) found from the chart?"],"metadata":{"id":"2cELzS2fp1cl"}},{"cell_typ